description:
The Roses, Barbara (Kathleen Turner) and Oliver (Michael Douglas), live happily as a married couple. Then she starts to wonder what life would be like without Oliver, and likes what she sees. Both want to stay in the house, and so they begin a campaign to force each other to leave. In the middle of the fighting is D&amp;#039;Amato (Danny DeVito), the divorce lawyer. He gets to see how far both will go to get rid of the other, and boy do they go far.. 
